{"tid":472800,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG DISPLAY將停止LCD面板投資：全力開發OLED","createTime":"2017-11-18T14:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T16:26:33.000Z","uid":47132,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d35b5b790c07afccc841c8d210d4a81d63afd9b3","tid":472800,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"據韓國商報報導，LG最近關閉了位於Gumi（龜尾市）的5代線P4工廠，這是繼3.5代線P2工廠後又一個關閉的LCD產線。預計在年底前，4代線P3工廠也將關閉。<br />\n按照LG Display副主席Han Sang-beom的說法，就公司目前而言，已經不會再對LCD技術做任何投資。而在2020年之前，他們預計將拿出總計約1200億人民幣用於OLED的研發和生產，包括但不限於Paju的P10/E6產線，龜尾和廣州的E5產線。LG目前沒有透露關閉的工廠會作何調整，但觀察人士普遍認為，會基於現有設備升級改造，轉投OLED。近日LG旗下公司LG顯示第三季度運營利潤將同比大增了80%，這樣的成績也遠遠超出了之前分析人士的預計。有傳言表示，LG在2018年的時候就可以給iPhone供應部分OLED螢幕。"},{"pid":"c0c0b97d02b183b646713ccac5d51c0992c92700","tid":472800,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"7539485e0a12b438f1e75bf2525a13da577357ea","tid":472800,"uid":92477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"Samsung加夠產能嘅話<br />\nlg隻oled將會冇廠揀"},{"pid":"851a6dfdfd16d38cca21c459aa78dce5080d9265","tid":472800,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"Pixel 2 用 Samsung<br />\n<br />\nPixel 2 XL 用 LG"},{"pid":"e06293846c9ea34af1705f25a38a266018c66f69","tid":472800,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pixel 2 用 Samsung<br />\n<br />\nPixel 2 XL 用 LG</blockquote><br />\nPixel 2 XL更新完根本冇問題"},{"pid":"5e4074ea1d6e6cfcee5f119822956121872d459e","tid":472800,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據韓國商報報導，LG最近關閉了位於Gumi（龜尾市）的5代線P4工廠，這是繼3.5代線P2工廠後又一個關閉的LCD產線。預計在年底前，4代線P3工廠也將關閉。<br />\n按照LG Display副主席Han Sang-beom的說法，就公司目前而言，已經不會再對LCD技術做任何投資。而在2020年之前，他們預計將拿出總計約1200億人民幣用於OLED的研發和生產，包括但不限於Paju的P10/E6產線，龜尾和廣州的E5產線。LG目前沒有透露關閉的工廠會作何調整，但觀察人士普遍認為，會基於現有設備升級改造，轉投OLED。近日LG旗下公司LG顯示第三季度運營利潤將同比大增了80%，這樣的成績也遠遠超出了之前分析人士的預計。有傳言表示，LG在2018年的時候就可以給iPhone供應部分OLED螢幕。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左大寸數   55     65  70<br />\n<br />\n向細size開發42  46寸oled  拉低價錢"},{"pid":"2c85e1ca81fc52c279edbd3de1efb3449ca41a7f","tid":472800,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/232528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F232528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d6f73cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/232547_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F232547_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b5950083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/232559_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F232559_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=24367164&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17068a6c45cc7b3168f06e7504dee94fb7237b41","tid":472800,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"唔好啦屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}